1
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:10,490
Slow down. I’m dying

2
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:19,310
Can’t you start your morning running late? -Cut it out

3
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:27,360
How is Yezi lately?

4
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,000
Thank me first

5
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,310
I’m telling you now. Put down your fists

6
00:02:40,110 --> 00:02:42,300
I gave your phone number to her

7
00:02:42,610 --> 00:02:48,870
Now is her most vulnerable and needy time. Hurry and get her back

8
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:55,380
You are the man. -I did this for you

9
00:02:57,040 --> 00:03:03,430
You know, love itself is very complicated

10
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:06,850
You have to experience breakups and getting back together in love

11
00:03:07,140 --> 00:03:09,400
[08. I’m not letting you go]
You heard me? Xiang Zeyi

12
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:15,860
[08. I’m not letting you go]

13
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:31,620
No, I saw him -Zhuxuan -I saw him

14
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,180
Zhuxuan

15
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,900
What are you talking about?

16
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:42,030
Listen, how did you ask Zhang Daniao the other day?

17
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:46,110
What did he say? Did Xiang Zeyi come back or not? -Is Xiang Zeyi back in town?

18
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:48,490
I suspect that very much

19
00:03:48,490 --> 00:03:54,270
I asked Zhang Daniao but he was sure that Xiang didn’t come back

20
00:03:54,980 --> 00:03:56,630
Is he lying?

21
00:03:57,460 --> 00:04:00,010
Not likely as far as I know him

22
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:06,050
What do you know about him? He used fired chicken to get you in college

23
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,920
I’m telling you, man can be very complicated

24
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:16,390
Like Yuan Lang didn’t upset you to death in one date. You are the one to talk

25
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:28,580
Zhuxuan, what’s wrong with you? We’ve been asking you since noon

26
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,430
Can’t you just tell us?

27
00:04:31,050 --> 00:04:39,700
Zhuxuan, we’ll buy you something tasty later -Stop being upset and talk to us

28
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:45,370
Even Yezi is busy with college activities and can’t be with you, you don’t have to act like this

29
00:04:45,370 --> 00:04:47,350
Is there anything that can’t be solved by alcohol?

30
00:04:47,350 --> 00:04:49,700
If there is, just drink more

31
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:53,620
It’s about that Yuan Lang

32
00:04:54,690 --> 00:05:00,220
What’s about Yuan Lang? Did you fight?

33
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:08,110
I just don’t get it. People say you can gain something back if you give something out

34
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:12,960
I’m being so passionate to him that I feel like I can burn now

35
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:16,160
Why isn’t he reacting in any way?

36
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:20,070
He is so chill that sometimes I question if we are in a relationship

37
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:23,110
Do you want to hear my real thoughts about this?

38
00:05:23,110 --> 00:05:26,330
Don’t talk if you are not on my side, or I’ll be so frustrated

39
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:34,920
The thing is, I always believe that if you chose to give out, you can’t expect to gain the same back

40
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:42,620
Or you’ll always feel unfair and your relation will be worse

41
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:46,520
The single one talks like she knows about my pain -I

42
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:49,470
What did you fight over this time?

43
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:51,580
Over where we’d spend the weekend

44
00:05:53,030 --> 00:05:54,600
It’s very important

45
00:05:56,970 --> 00:05:59,910
I asked him like, where do we spend the weekend?

46
00:05:59,910 --> 00:06:05,490
Shouldn’t he at least ask where do I want to go? Guess what he said

47
00:06:05,490 --> 00:06:10,270
Generally, people need to rest in weekends

48
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:15,970
If people choose to go out in that period of time, there will be traffic in our city

49
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:20,140
So we’ll have to spend 30% of our time on road

50
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:25,090
If we choose to go to public places like movie theater

51
00:06:25,090 --> 00:06:31,350
We’ll have to spend another 30% of time on waiting in line

52
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:35,330
And the last 40% of time will be very precious to us

53
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:39,660
We may not have time to eat or rest

54
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:45,580
So as far as I say, staying in home is our best choice

55
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:49,730
Or we can go outside of town to walk and relax

56
00:06:56,030 --> 00:07:00,560
What this kind of boyfriend needs is a hard punch so he’ll remembers

57
00:07:00,850 --> 00:07:06,040
I really can’t bear with his legal medical major nor with him being that rational

58
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:09,140
Nor with his rationally analyzing our date

59
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:13,350
Shouldn’t love be irrational, blind and crazy?

60
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:19,240
But that’s the man you fell for

61
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:24,620
Maybe you are exploding here but he doesn’t even know why you are upset

62
00:07:24,890 --> 00:07:31,360
Cheng Xi is right this time. He might think you are being brutal and unreasonable -Right

63
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:39,580
Stop being upset, let’s go eat something nice -Right, let’s just eat

64
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:44,920
And let the desperating straight guy rationally figure out why you are being upset

65
00:07:50,170 --> 00:07:54,400
Hello -You mom asked me to bring you this -Thanks

66
00:07:54,710 --> 00:07:58,480
I told her you are busy with school activities -Yes, our team is going to Nanjing for three days

67
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,680
Exhausting

68
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:04,230
One more thing. I have to do what I was asked to do

69
00:08:04,530 --> 00:08:08,450
Someone asked you. Yuan Lang?

70
00:08:08,770 --> 00:08:13,340
He said that he didn’t what he did to upset Zhuxuan -I knew it

71
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:15,800
What? -Nothing.

72
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:23,510
I can talk to Zhuxuan, but it’s still about them two. It’s best for us to stay back

73
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,060
What about

74
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,820
What about you and Xiang Zeyi?

75
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,610
Good, why?

76
00:08:33,580 --> 00:08:38,850
Nothing. It was your choice, as long as you are happy with it

77
00:08:40,090 --> 00:08:41,780
Thanks

78
00:08:58,470 --> 00:08:59,730
Thank you

79
00:09:05,540 --> 00:09:10,740
Hello -What are you doing? -Packing. Call you later

80
00:09:11,010 --> 00:09:14,480
Packing. Where are you going?

81
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:21,230
Sorry, I forgot to tell you. It’s the activity that our college organized. I’m going to Nanjing

82
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:29,620
Fine. Travel safe -OK I’ll call you

83
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,350
More? That many

84
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:42,910
What activity? Why didn’t she tell me?

85
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:48,860
Xiang Zeyi

86
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:59,840
What do you need from a man with girlfriend, in such middle of night, under boys’ dormitory?

87
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,570
Isn’t this misleading to others?

88
00:10:02,810 --> 00:10:08,600
Is it more misleading than a boy and a girl always meeting alone in dark?

89
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:18,670
Look, these two are often seeing each other under dormitory building

90
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:22,250
I don’t need to describe their dubious expressions

91
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:28,120
Is this all you got? -What?

92
00:10:29,510 --> 00:10:32,570
Lin Sen and Yezi have been good friends for ever

93
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:37,760
It’s normal for them to talk, let alone I believe in my choice, I believe in Yezi

94
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,290
Xiang Zeyi you

95
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:42,020
Stop doing things like this

96
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,810
Embarrassing

97
00:11:07,050 --> 00:11:13,250
Time to get up

98
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:18,120
Come on not again -Liu, get up to do good things. To excise to run

99
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:22,280
We need to have good habits and to be the best version of ourselves

100
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:26,880
Get up now -Zhuxuan cut it out

101
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:38,220
What?

102
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:43,020
You look like a little aggrieved bride

103
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:59,880
Yezi is gone, it’s only us three. Eat as much as you can, this meal is on me

104
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,120
Eat, why are you counting?

105
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:25,400
It’s so windy outside, I’m here to hide, will you take me, pretty girls?

106
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:47,920
(In Japanese) Greetings, I am Zhuxuan

107
00:12:57,310 --> 00:12:58,430
99

108
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:02,110
100

109
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:06,390
It’s still early, why don’t we call Yezi?

110
00:13:07,810 --> 00:13:12,850
Zhuxuan I’m warning you, Yezi is busy with collage activities, leave her alone

111
00:13:12,850 --> 00:13:16,210
Say one more word and I’ll pull your tongue out

112
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:23,230
Zhuxuan we are begging you, we are just normal people, not as energetic as you

113
00:13:23,230 --> 00:13:29,940
Can you leave us be? -Just go to sleep. We have Prof.Chen’s morning roll call tomorrow

114
00:13:42,410 --> 00:13:43,330
Hello

115
00:13:43,930 --> 00:13:48,260
Hello, what’s your name, please? And what’s your story?

116
00:13:48,530 --> 00:13:53,080
I fell in love with a man but I didn’t know that he was married

117
00:13:55,870 --> 00:14:00,040
So what what do you want to talk about?

118
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:06,050
Here is the thing. I am sophomore of our college, I fell in love with a man

119
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:14,370
Who is 20 years older than me -God. What are you going to do?

120
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:24,200
But I didn’t know about this when I decided to be with him

121
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:29,970
I thought he was single, I didn’t know he has a family -Is it the thing?

122
00:14:29,970 --> 00:14:34,760
Yes, and I’m just a college student, I haven’t entered to the society -Zhuxuan

123
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,030
Hello

124
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:43,450
Are you still there?

125
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:58,950
No, disaster -Zhuxuan are you done yet? I’m telling you, stop disturbing my sleep now

126
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:02,250
I really heard something out there

127
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:10,990
I heard it too -I told you

128
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:14,190
Sounds like someone crying

129
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,200
It must be that

130
00:15:20,990 --> 00:15:22,350
What?

131
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:29,300
Do you know where the little road behind the building leads to?

132
00:15:29,610 --> 00:15:31,970
To the back door of our school -Wrong

133
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:40,200
It’s the road of postgraduate recommendation

134
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,930
You guys

135
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:49,580
Cold-blooded

136
00:16:13,430 --> 00:16:17,110
You hurt me and laugh it out

137
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:20,740
I love you and I’m being a coward

138
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:23,640
Tears in my eyes -I’m back

139
00:16:23,990 --> 00:16:33,590
Yezi finally you are back -What happened? -Yezi, you are back

140
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:37,630
I missed you to death -What’s wrong?

141
00:16:38,250 --> 00:16:39,420
Pick out my heart

142
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:44,730
I lo-lo-love you

143
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:51,780
My love lasts for ever and ever -Come here

144
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:54,380
Being in love is so

145
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:59,620
I’m sad -And heavy

146
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:08,750
Go go go

147
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:26,370
Lin Sen

148
00:17:26,670 --> 00:17:28,170
What did you call me for?

149
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:32,190
Can you ask out Yuan Lang for me? -Why?

150
00:17:32,570 --> 00:17:37,690
I just came back from Nanjing and I realize that Zhuxuan is almost crazy

151
00:17:37,690 --> 00:17:45,410
And she is making us crazy too. It can’t last longer. We almost got punished last night

152
00:17:45,410 --> 00:17:49,170
That serious? -Or I won’t ask for your help

153
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:56,570
What these two need is real communication, it’s far from principled problems

154
00:17:56,570 --> 00:17:59,790
That why my Shige (senior fellow apprentice) is like lost his mind lately

155
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:04,500
I’ll ask him out for you -Thanks then -How do you thank me?

156
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:06,840
How do you want me to? Ask Zhu to buy you dishes

157
00:18:15,420 --> 00:18:16,480
Come with me

158
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:19,160
What are you doing? Let me go

159
00:18:21,090 --> 00:18:25,030
Why didn’t you tell me that you are back? -What’s wrong?

160
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:29,540
I think there is some misunderstanding between you two -Shut up

161
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:32,900
You didn’t tell me when you were gone, I understand that, you were busy

162
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:36,030
And you didn’t tell me that you are back but meet him first, what do you mean by that?

163
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:39,120
Xiang Zeyi, listen to me -This is between us two

164
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:44,960
Do you know you look like a crazy person right now?

165
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,670
OK

166
00:18:47,570 --> 00:18:51,820
All I need is an explanation, is it hard? -I have nothing to explain to you. I didn’t do anything wrong

167
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:54,900
Nothing wrong? Xu Wenjie told me that you two... -What did you just say?

168
00:18:57,020 --> 00:18:58,410
Xu Wenjie?

169
00:19:06,230 --> 00:19:09,030
Xiang Zeyi, I'm disappointed in you

170
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:14,500
You are the one to talk -Is this what you are thinking? -You

171
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:17,200
Lin Sen let’s go -Come back

172
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:20,330
What do you mean? -What do you mean?

173
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:23,850
I am your girlfriend but you choose to believe her over me? -I

174
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:31,620
Right. I freaking believed you too much to see your little scene today

175
00:19:33,890 --> 00:19:36,840
Are you treating Yezi fairly? -None of your business -What are you doing?

176
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:39,020
You annoy me -You annoy me too

177
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:41,900
Stop it

178
00:19:42,930 --> 00:19:44,430
Stop it

179
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:50,060
Tear off your fake and pretentious mask -Break off your dirty and shameless hands -Stop it

180
00:20:01,690 --> 00:20:03,420
Why didn’t you go to Lin Sen?

181
00:20:18,450 --> 00:20:21,450
Does it hurt? -No

182
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,740
Why did you poke me so hard?

183
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,420
Do you have anything else to say?

184
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:37,480
You didn’t look handsome at all when you fought -What?

185
00:20:42,140 --> 00:20:46,700
Are you saying he looked better than me when fought? -He looked worse than you

186
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:48,970
Worse than me

187
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,980
So I looked better than him

188
00:20:58,670 --> 00:21:01,890
I know, it was my bad

189
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:07,900
But believe me, I didn’t listen at all when Xu Wenjie talked to me

190
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:12,610
I was just

191
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:20,980
You looked so happy when you were talking to Lin Sen, so I felt weird and went crazy

192
00:21:23,690 --> 00:21:29,100
I didn’t do well either. I didn’t explain to you in calmer way

193
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:35,770
I know you got upset because you cared about me, about us

194
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:41,770
But, your doubts about us need to be punished

195
00:21:47,790 --> 00:21:54,760
Thank you for your mercy your highness -Let’s see how much you can owe me

196
00:22:00,540 --> 00:22:04,870
Are we good now? -You look dirty

197
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:14,420
Let’s go -Are you disliking me? -I am -Then don’t come for me -I’m leaving -Whatever

198
00:22:14,870 --> 00:22:24,320
Are you leaving? -Leaving -I’m leaving -I am -Come here

199
00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:28,960
Take care of uncle, I’ll go check on other patients

200
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:30,380
Call me if you need me

201
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:49,770
Dad you are awake, how do you feel?

202
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:54,190
I’ll go call the doctor -My girl

203
00:23:56,080 --> 00:24:03,880
It was my bad. I made you worried for long, sorry my precious girl

204
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:24,340
Mom, dad has awaken, he is fine now -Thanks to God. I’ll bring you dishes later

205
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:29,140
No need to hurry, I’m here with him

206
00:24:29,470 --> 00:24:33,480
OK, remember to rest yourself -I will

207
00:24:57,090 --> 00:25:04,630
Excuse me, do you know who brought these fruits over? -Tall and handsome

208
00:25:04,630 --> 00:25:09,410
He looked better than Doctor Lin -No, Doctor Lin is more handsome

209
00:26:54,580 --> 00:26:55,740
Xiang Zeyi

210
00:27:09,190 --> 00:27:10,960
Why did you leave me?

211
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:21,080
Why did you disappear without telling anyone? Tell me why?

212
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:51,200
Leave

213
00:28:25,660 --> 00:28:30,120
I will make you keep your promises. I’m not giving up on you
